30 (A) Convicted as an adult under the Kansas criminal code;
31 (B) sentenced as an adult under the Kansas criminal code following
32 termination of status as an extended jurisdiction juvenile pursuant to
33 K.S.A. 38-2364, and amendments thereto; or
